# cmd

**Instance Property**

Common to all load command structures. For this structure, set to either `LC_LOAD_DYLIB`, `LC_LOAD_WEAK_DYLIB`, or `LC_ID_DYLIB`.

## Declaration

```swift
uint32_t cmd;
```
